
This directory contains commented examples using BGWpy.
It is recommendent to run these examples in numeral order.

The input and output files created can be compared with the corresponding 
files in Reference/.

The binary files of Quantum Espresso and BerkeleyGW must be available from
your PATH environment variable in order for the example to run successfully.

You might have to edit the scripts to adapt the MPI options
to your local environment.

